  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 17th level, your control of time has reached it's peak. Once per long rest, you can spend 15 chakra to pause time. You stop time for everyone but yourself for 1d4+1 turns. During this time, you can move and act as normal. This feature ends if you move a creature(Other than yourself) more than 30 feet from their original position or deal damage to a creature within the stopped time. within the stopped time. Anything you do, whether it be damage or some other effect cannot be reacted to. In addition, this feature ends if you move to a place more than 1,000 feet from the location where you activated it.</p>",
